# Welcome to Shwoop!

The Shwoop AUT Games week has begun! 
Keep an eye on the app over the week as more challenges are released with bigger and better prizes. 

If you are using an iPhone, ensure you are updated to iOS 13 for the best experience. 
If you've found the solution but your app isn't working, send us a selfie at the location on messenger. 

Send any questions or selfies here. 

 [https://www.facebook.com/shwoopnz/](https://www.facebook.com/shwoopnz/).

# 3x $99 Headphones

AUT Riff Off

12.30pm Hikuwai Plaza 

[Headover To The Shwoop Event Page.](https://www.facebook.com/events/638009066606335/)

![the market banner](https://uoa-bs-maps.s3-ap-southeast-2.amazonaws.com/The-Market-Logo.png)

# $500 The Market Gift Card

Take 15 seconds to enter your details and go in the draw to win a $500 shopoing spree from The Market

[Follow This Link To The Market](https://themarket.com/about/aut-shwoop/?utm_source=aut_shwoop&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=500_dollar_giveaway&fbclid=IwAR1-_eVh9CqwZqrYgmH0coVAt44cCQQ8Iw3SJ01Bo00kgSwQTDxmNoQZrXs)

# Make Me Laugh

At 12PM you you will find a shwoopian in purple here in Hikuwai Plaza.
Make them laugh and win a prize!
